WEBVTT

1
00:00:00,784 --> 00:00:03,581
<i>The thing that I love about Superman is,</i>

2
00:00:03,633 --> 00:00:07,940
<i>no matter how dark or cynical
the world gets,</i>

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:11,716
<i>he always is hopeful
and heroic and optimistic.</i>

4
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:13,629
He's a blue sky superhero.

5
00:00:13,630 --> 00:00:15,669
<i>[DRAMATIC MUSIC]</i>

6
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:17,599
He's a man who could do anything,

7
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,469
<i>and he's choosing to fight for us.</i>

8
00:00:19,470 --> 00:00:21,439
When Superman wins the day,

9
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:23,540
<i>you feel like you won the day.</i>

10
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:26,239
I think every major creator
at some point

11
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:28,109
<i>wants to tell a Superman story.</i>

12
00:00:28,110 --> 00:00:30,079
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:32,549
"Krypton" to me is such a vibrant idea

14
00:00:32,550 --> 00:00:34,719
<i>because there's so little
that's been explored.</i>

15
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:36,349
To be a part of something
that's just got

16
00:00:36,350 --> 00:00:37,940
such a massive legacy to it,

17
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:39,559
<i>it's very surreal.</i>

18
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:43,460
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19
