Hi, I'm Cameron Cuffe
from the new show "Krypton,"

21
00:00:50,380 --> 00:00:53,389
and right now, I'm in Belfast,
standing on our version

22
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:55,289
<i>of the Fortress of Solitude.</i>

